#
# File: getintfdets
# Helper script for reporting interface details
#
# Author: Paul Walker
#
# Copyright: Sixnet 2012
#
# Details: This script is called by gau screen dispintfdets to report interface 
# details for switch and non-switch devices. If model_name, as reported by
# getfc, is of the form "BT-##21", this script will call intfdetssnwrpt to
# report snswrpt for a switch device. ethtool will be called for any other
# model names.

#deal with SN-, BT-, RAM-, LALA-, ANY-

modelNo="$(skvs get FC_MODELNO | sed -e 's/[A-Z]*-[0-9][0-9]\(\S*\).*/\1/g')"
case "$modelNo" in
        21)
                ../bin/intfdetssnswrpt
                ;;
        *)
                ../bin/intfdetsethtool
                ;;
esac
